. Umar announced\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39783,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/18\/umar-ii-on-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":39808,"position":1},"title":"Umar II on Qadr: O Allah, content me with Your divine decree","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Sa\u2019id reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, would supplicate often, saying, \u201cO Allah, make me pleased with Your decree and bless me in Your providence, such that I would not like to hasten anything You delay, nor delay anything You hasten.\u201d Source: al-Rid\u0323a\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20779,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/26\/umar-shows-me-my-faults\/","url_meta":{"origin":39808,"position":2},"title":"Umar II on Humility: Allah have mercy on one who shows me my flaws","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 26, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Kalabadhi reported: Umar ibn Abdul Aziz, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cMay Allah have mercy on a man who shows me my faults.\u201d Source: Bah\u0323r al-Fawa\u0304\u02bcid 1\/129 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0643\u0644\u0627\u0628\u0627\u0630\u064a \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064f \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0639\u064e\u063